Conduct qualitative and quantitative research on labor market information including; economic market conditions and trends in employment, unemployment, earnings, and job openings;
Analysis on size and composition of the local economy, including demographic characteristics;
current and future workforce demand and supply, including current and projected information about industry and occupational employment, job creation and destruction, the types of work available, and the skills gap analysis;
