Position Description
We are seeking a highly motivated and experienced Bioinformatics Scientist in the Department of Research and Development. The successful candidate will focus on the analysis of large NGS datasets with in-depth knowledge of data-handling and sufficient knowledge of cancer genomics. This position will provide ample opportunities for professional development and the acquisition of cutting-edge skills in basic and translational cancer genomics research, research planning and strategy, and data analysis and interpretation.
